title: Obama celebrates American music with 'eclectic bunch'
text:
> Entertainment Obama celebrates American music with 'eclectic bunch' President Barack Obama walks onto the stage in the East Room of the White House in Washington at the beginning of the "In Performance at the White House" series, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015. This event, “A Celebration of American Creativity" will celebrate the 50th anniversary of the National Foundation on the Arts and the Humanities Act.
